@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - Inventory

[*] --> AddNewGoods
state "Add new goods" as AddNewGoods
state "Update price" as UpdatePrice
state "Remove goods" as RemoveGoods
state "Identify expired goods" as IdentifyExpiredGoods
state "Notify user" as NotifyUser
state "Place order" as PlaceOrder
state "Generate invoice" as GenerateInvoice
state "Search items" as SearchItems
state "Select items for purchase" as SelectItemsForPurchase
state "Calculate discount and tax" as CalculateDiscountAndTax
state "Generate receipt" as GenerateReceipt
state "Replace item or cancel receipt" as ReplaceItemOrCancelReceipt
state "Record customer requests" as RecordCustomerRequests
state "View summary report" as ViewSummaryReport

AddNewGoods --> UpdatePrice : new goods added
UpdatePrice --> RemoveGoods : price updated
RemoveGoods --> IdentifyExpiredGoods : goods removed
IdentifyExpiredGoods --> NotifyUser : expired goods identified
NotifyUser --> PlaceOrder : notify user to place order
PlaceOrder --> GenerateInvoice : generate invoice for order
GenerateInvoice --> SearchItems : search items available in inventory
SearchItems --> SelectItemsForPurchase : select items for purchase
SelectItemsForPurchase --> CalculateDiscountAndTax : calculate discount and tax
CalculateDiscountAndTax --> GenerateReceipt : generate receipt for customer
GenerateReceipt --> ReplaceItemOrCancelReceipt : replace item or cancel receipt if needed
ReplaceItemOrCancelReceipt --> RecordCustomerRequests : record customer requests
RecordCustomerRequests --> ViewSummaryReport : view summary report of all transactions

ViewSummaryReport --> [*]

@enduml
